    "rationale": "12 of 13 credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by the strength of the multi-laboratory, multi-specimen validation dataset and the conservative acceptance bounds applied. Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk, Medium decision consequence COU. Package accepted with acknowledgment of the test conditions gap.",
